== Overview ==

Dragon Quest I & II features magic spells for the Hero (DQ1) and for the Prince of Cannock and Princess of Moonbrooke (DQ2). This page documents all spells and their mechanics.

== Spell Data Structure ==

Each spell entry is 6 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Spell ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || MP cost
|-
| $02 || 1 || Effect type
|-
| $03 || 1 || Power value
|-
| $04 || 1 || Target type
|-
| $05 || 1 || Flags (battle/field)
|}

